songs.title: X Chords
songs.lyrics:
[Instrumental with scattered singing]

And how she wants this to evolve
The very fact that I'm saying these things in a- it is a sign of sophistication and growth!
People couldn't say this ten years ago!
And people are listening
A third of the people that listen to this are gonna think it over and are going to take some steps in, uh, in self-actualization
